     8‚Üí/**
     9‚Üí * Psychoacoustic Masking Engine - Phase 1 Implementation
    10‚Üí * 
    11‚Üí * Implements perceptual masking thresholds using Bark/ERB band analysis with
    12‚Üí * strict RT-safety guarantees and locked mathematical formulas.
    13‚Üí * 
    14‚Üí * Mathematical Pipeline (locked - do not modify):
    15‚Üí * 1) Compress:     Uk = |Xk|^Œ±  where Œ± ‚àà {1.0, 0.6}
    16‚Üí * 2) Pool:         Eb = Œ£k Wk,b ¬∑ Uk
    17‚Üí * 3) Spread:       Mb = Œ£b0 Sb0‚Üíb ¬∑ Eb0   (asymmetric)
    18‚Üí * 4) Expand:       Tb = Mb^(1/Œ±) + ATHb
    19‚Üí * 5) Back-project: Tk = Œ£b Wk,b ¬∑ Tb
    20‚Üí * 
    21‚Üí * JND Clamping: g' = min(g, Amax_k / (Ak + Œµ))
    22‚Üí * where Amax_k = m ¬∑ sqrt(c ¬∑ Tk)
    23‚Üí * 
    24‚Üí * Performance Optimizations:
    25‚Üí * - Fast Œ±-law using exp2/log2 instead of std::pow
    26‚Üí * - FTZ/DAZ denormal handling
    27‚Üí * - 64-byte aligned SIMD-ready buffers
